---
title: Cheesy BBQ Chicken & Chorizo Enchiladas with Cucumber Salsa & Yoghurt
description: Cheese is the key to almost everything, but these enchiladas are packed with Cheddar cheese and a variety of other tasty additions. Bite in and discover the saucy chicken and chorizo with veggies hidden inside. On the outside the cheese is melted over and cooled down with a dollop of yoghurt.
